txt.en: 'We have heard that The Scourge has sent Corsair forces into Tarlang's Crown. While we are still unsure of their purpose there, I do not wish to wait to find out.\n\n'Travel to Tarlang's Crown and defeat the Corsairs there. However, I would not go alone if I were you... you would do well to gather your allies before setting off!'
Elaglar can be found in Dol Amroth.\n\nYou have slain many Corsairs and should now report to Elaglar.
The Corsairs of Umbar work in service of The Scourge and his ally, Azruthor, in Tarlang's Crown and present a constant threat to the people of Gondor.
Tarlang's Crown - Servants of the Heirs
'Their numbers may recover in time, but you have dealt them a harsh blow this day!'
Corsairs can be found throughout Tarlang's Crown.\n\nElaglar has asked you to thin the numbers of the Corsair forces in Tarlang's Crown.
